usdInternetAgent.name: usdInternetAgent

revisions.description: Obsoleted the QoS related objects in the Unisphere-Data-IP-MIB.
The initial release of this management information module.

usdInternetAgent.contactinfo: Unisphere Networks, Inc. Postal: 10 Technology Park Drive Westford, MA 01886 USA Tel: +1 978 589 5800 E-mail: mib@UnisphereNetworks.com
usdInternetAgent.description: The agent capabilities definitions for the basic layer 3 and 4 Internet component of the SNMP agent in the Unisphere Routing Switch family of products.

usdInternetAgentV1.name: usdInternetAgentV1
usdInternetAgentV1.productrelease:
Version 1 of the Internet component of the Unisphere Routing Switch
        SNMP agent.  This version of the Internet component was supported in the
        Unisphere 2.x system releases.
usdInternetAgentV1.description: The MIBs supported by the SNMP agent for the Internet application in the Unisphere Routing Switch. These capabilities became obsolete when the IP global objects were added to the Unisphere-Data-IP-MIB.

usdInternetAgentV2.name: usdInternetAgentV2
usdInternetAgentV2.productrelease:
Version 2 of the Internet component of the Unisphere Routing Switch
        SNMP agent.  This version of the Internet component was supported in the
        Unisphere RX 3.0 and RX 3.1 system releases.
usdInternetAgentV2.description: The MIBs supported by the SNMP agent for the Internet application in the Unisphere Routing Switch. These capabilities became obsolete when support was added for the RFC1213-MIB.ipRouteTable and the Unisphere-Data-IP-MIB.rsIpIfAssocTable.

usdInternetAgentV3.name: usdInternetAgentV3
usdInternetAgentV3.productrelease:
Version 3 of the Internet component of the Unisphere Routing Switch
        SNMP agent.  This version of the Internet component was supported in the
        Unisphere RX 3.2 and subsequent 3.x system releases.
usdInternetAgentV3.description: The MIBs supported by the SNMP agent for the Internet application in the Unisphere Routing Switch. These capabilities became obsolete when the QoS related objects in the Unisphere-Data-IP-MIB were obsoleted.

usdInternetAgentV4.name: usdInternetAgentV4
usdInternetAgentV4.productrelease:
Version 4 of the Internet component of the Unisphere Routing Switch
        SNMP agent.  This version of the Internet component is supported in the
        Unisphere RX 4.0 and subsequent system releases.
usdInternetAgentV4.description: The MIBs supported by the SNMP agent for the Internet application in the Unisphere Routing Switch.
